data.description: Beautiful Home in Eastbrook School District!  Plenty of Space Inside & Out!  4 Bedrooms & 3 Full Baths! Over 2 Acres of Stunning Views with Mature Trees to Enjoy! The Property Offers Your Own Peace of Paradise and is Located on a Very Welcoming Country Road. Large Dining Room & Custom Kitchen with Island Offering Plenty of Cabinets & Countertops.  All Appliances Remain! Living Room is the Perfect Space with Plenty of Sunlight and Room to Relax. Gorgeous Full Bath with Walk-in Shower on Main Level.    Upper Level Offers 3 Additional Bedrooms, 2 Full Baths, & Utility Room with Washer/Dryer that Remain.  Brand New Carpet Upper Level.  This Home Was Completely Remodeled in 2018 With NEW NEW NEW!  Roof, Windows, AC, Furnace, Water Heater, Water Softener all only 5 Years old!! Large Detached Garage with Plenty of Room to Play! Nice Covered Porch in the Front and Back. Beautiful Property!  This One is an Absolute Must See!
